Tattooed Man
A warrior marked by magical tattoos that grant extraordinary abilities. Each
tattoo is a living enchantment drawn with PPE: weapon tattoos summon blades
of force, armor tattoos generate protective fields, power tattoos grant sight,
stealth, or healing. The Tattooed Man is a walking arsenal of living magic.

Unlike the Tattoo Warrior (who is Atlantean-only), the Tattooed Man OCC is
open to any race flagged as tattoo-capable or with special access. They use
their body as their weapon, shunning most technology in favour of ancient
Atlantean magic arts. Skill picks come from Physical, Weapons, and Wilderness.

Attribute requirements: None.
PPE: Moderate pool fuels tattoo activation.
Starting equipment: Light body armor, one weapon of choice, 4-6 starting
tattoos inscribed by an Atlantean Tattoo Master.

